Copy this file to `.env` (same folder) so server/index.js can pick these up.
Both are optional individually, but each unlocks a different feature. Paste
your own value after each equals sign below - leave blank to skip that one.

# --- Nutrition data (USDA FoodData Central) - free ---
# Sign up: https://fdc.nal.usda.gov/api-key-signup/
# Without this, nutrition lookups still work via USDA's public DEMO_KEY
# (30 requests/hour, 50/day) - fine for trying things out.
USDA_FDC_API_KEY=

# --- Chat assistant (OpenAI) - pay-per-use ---
# Get a key: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# Without this, the Chat tab explains it isn't configured yet - there's no
# free fallback for this one.
OPENAI_API_KEY=

# Optional: use a different OpenAI model (defaults to gpt-4o-mini).
# OPENAI_CHAT_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini

# Optional: change the port the proxy server listens on.
# NUTRITION_PROXY_PORT=8787
